It is rather interesting. 
While they talk about cutting taxes, here is one where they arrange to tax mostly young people. 
A tax is added to the earnings of a person living in a home with his or her parents. 
Those earnings are added to the income of the parent claiming an exemption. 
They introduced a tax on passive income. 
